Havoc Silver Eau de Toilette - 75 ml Price: Rs.699

Excellent perfum to make your body fresh & germless. Cologne spray with long time stay smell. Havoc is classified as a gorgeous powdery mossy green aldehydic chypre with a floral that begins with a tantalizing floral creme broule. It gradually settles down to a really lovely retro mix of green floracy and a faint musk. It is a very rare and hard to find perfume. This fragrance was originally produced back in the 1970's by mary quant. Havoc silver a bottle of 75 ml with a tempting smell.
